data.eml:eml: First inventory of sea anemones (Cnidaria: Actiniaria) from La Paz Bay, southern Gulf of California (Mexico)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Barragán, Yamaly, Sánchez, Carlos, Rodríguez, Estefanía (2019): First inventory of sea anemones (Cnidaria: Actiniaria) from La Paz Bay, southern Gulf of California (Mexico). Zootaxa 4559 (3): 501-549, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4559.3.4
